474
00:21:31,030 --> 00:21:32,920
That's right. Keep your voice down.

475
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:35,080
We must keep an eye on it this time.

476
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,870
We won't sell it if it's anything less than 100.

477
00:21:37,870 --> 00:21:38,220
Yes.

478
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:40,000
When we're all rich,

479
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:40,750
all of you

480
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:43,150
