481
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,630
Great!

482
00:21:44,630 --> 00:21:45,240
Ling.

483
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,150
Go make two cheongsams.

484
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:47,560
Okay.

485
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,040
