486
00:21:49,770 --> 00:21:50,530
As for me...

487
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:51,640
I'm going to

488
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:53,850
renovate this room slightly.

489
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,400
It's our façade.

490
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:56,950
That's right.

491
00:21:57,980 --> 00:21:59,800
I shouldn't be making this fortune alone.

492
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:02,250
We should all reap our own dividends, right?

493
00:22:02,250 --> 00:22:03,640
Thank you, Ms. Zhou.

494
00:22:04,210 --> 00:22:06,100
