516
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:46,150
Wei, you're back.

517
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:46,960
You guys...

518
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:48,400
We've dumped them all.

519
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,660
Yeah, dumped them all.

520
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:51,470
Wen?

521
00:22:51,490 --> 00:22:53,150
Yes, I've dumped them all too.

522
00:22:53,930 --> 00:22:54,650
You guys...

523
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:56,230
We've also dumped them all.

524
00:23:00,360 --> 00:23:02,280
Any insider information?

525
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,880
There's too much hype around

526
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,190
