533
00:23:21,450 --> 00:23:22,540
Yes, we did.

534
00:23:22,570 --> 00:23:23,230
Yes, we've really dumped them all.

535
00:23:23,230 --> 00:23:24,620
Yes.

536
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:25,800
Okay.

537
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:39,320
Ms. Zhou, why don't you quickly help us dump them?

538
00:23:39,320 --> 00:23:40,280
We've earned enough.

539
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:40,960
That's right.

540
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:41,850
Don't worry.

541
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,760
