542
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:44,650
It's all ready.

543
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:46,640
I'll dump it away when it hits 100, okay?

544
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,560
Okay, fine.

545
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:48,530
Okay, that's it.

546
00:23:48,530 --> 00:23:49,720
Let's all go to bed.

547
00:23:54,080 --> 00:23:55,280
The papers these days

548
