00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:38,240
That's how he rules over them.

568
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:40,520
It's ridiculous and pathetic.

569
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:43,560
I don't think it's

570
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,540
going to be easy to recover

571
