This process is very painful.

579
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,630
We all have feelings.

580
00:25:04,020 --> 00:25:05,950
Only by personally experiencing,

581
00:25:06,470 --> 00:25:07,390
reflecting,

582
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,600
and thinking,

583
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:12,310
can we climb out of the ruins of so-called faith,

584
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,650
and better cherish the light

585
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:16,240
in the darkness.

586
00:25:23,010 --> 00:25:25,510
[One month later]

587
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,640
Sir.

588
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,220
We need to start taking precautions.

589
00:25:31,220 --> 00:25:32,610
If someone starts to sell short,

590
00:25:32,610 --> 00:25:34,310
it's bound to cause a panic sell-off.

591
00:25:34,310 --> 00:25:35,310
They dare not.

592
00:25:35,530 --> 00:25:36,930
Why would they not?

593
00:25:36,950 --> 00:25:39,210
They've made a lot of money in this round.

594
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:41,470
That's precisely why there's no need for them to sell short.

595
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:43,470
They've earned money from the bank.

596
00:25:43,490 --> 00:25:45,130
Why would there be a need to hurt the people again?

597
00:25:45,130 --> 00:25:47,180
Besides, ruining the treasury securities

598
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:47,880
will affect the overall situation.

599
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:49,400
Nanjing will not agree.

600
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:52,120
Don't worry.

601
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:54,160
I won't give them a chance to sell short.

602
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,860
We're the Central Bank. Besides money,

603
00:25:55,860 --> 00:25:57,920
we are also protected by law and guns.

604
00:25:58,420 --> 00:25:59,220
Trust me.

605
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:34,000
That's all for today.

606
00:26:34,080 --> 00:26:36,260
The market is closed. Come again tomorrow.

607
00:26:36,260 --> 00:26:37,520
Don't worry, Mr. Song.

608
00:26:37,670 --> 00:26:39,640
I know you're worried about the market overheating.

609
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:40,400
But today,

610
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:41,280
I've gathered

611
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:42,080
all the banks,

612
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,920
and asked them to lock the warehouse

613
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:44,830
immediately after closing.

614
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,310
They are not allowed to sell for the next five years.

615
00:26:46,310 --> 00:26:47,620
This will stabilize the price of the treasury bills

616
00:26:47,620 --> 00:26:49,460
within a reasonable range.

617
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:52,290
[Locking up the warehouse to control prices]

618
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,230
I know.

619
00:26:50,260 --> 00:26:52,720
Locking up the warehouse to control prices.

620
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:55,810
Locking up the warehouse to control prices?

621
00:26:55,810 --> 00:26:58,170
He's too naive.

622
00:26:58,660 --> 00:27:01,430
The Treasury Department has officially issued a statement today

623
00:27:01,430 --> 00:27:02,630
to clarify the rumor.

624
00:27:03,050 --> 00:27:06,180
They have no plans to recall the treasury bills in advance.

625
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:07,910
Once this news gets out,

626
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:10,170
the price of the treasury bills...

627
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:14,680
With this undertaking, the banks

628
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,750
will be spitting out all the money

629
00:27:16,750 --> 00:27:18,710
they've earned in the past few years,

630
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:20,570
and may have to even make up for it.

631
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:24,730
After you finish profiteering off the banks, the next should be the retail investors, right?

632
00:27:24,730 --> 00:27:27,190
We've already made almost twice the profit.

633
00:27:27,290 --> 00:27:29,310
In my opinion, the time has come.

634
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,700
When trading begins tomorrow,

635
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:34,030
let's use the money we've earn to short it,

636
00:27:34,080 --> 00:27:35,980
and make twice as much of what we already have.

637
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:36,980
What do you think?

638
00:27:37,490 --> 00:27:38,450
Sure.

639
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:39,430
Of course.

640
00:27:58,640 --> 00:27:59,120
Tunan.

641
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:00,120
Mr. Song.

642
00:28:01,050 --> 00:28:03,370
Get rid of all your treasury bills.

643
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,680
I don't think that's right.

644
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:07,320
We agreed to lock the warehouse today.

645
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:08,120
Don't ask too many questions.

646
00:28:08,120 --> 00:28:08,530
Dump them all!

647
00:28:08,530 --> 00:28:09,390
But Mr. Song...

648
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:46,630
Sir.

649
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:48,970
The movement of the construction treasury bill is very odd today.

650
00:28:48,970 --> 00:28:50,710
It's going down as soon as market opened.

651
00:28:50,710 --> 00:28:51,990
Dump all the treasury bills.

652
00:28:51,990 --> 00:28:53,780
Dump as many as you can.

653
00:28:53,970 --> 00:28:55,150
Shouldn't we be locking the warehouse instead?

654
00:28:55,150 --> 00:28:56,890
If I tell you to dump it, just do as I say.

655
00:28:56,890 --> 00:28:57,570
Yes.

656
00:28:58,490 --> 00:28:59,020
Hurry!

657
00:28:59,130 --> 00:29:00,730
Dump all the treasury bills.

658
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:01,340
Dump them.

659
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:04,200
Sell it now! Someone's crashing the market!

660
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:04,700
No way.

661
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,150
Dump it!

662
00:29:05,150 --> 00:29:06,200
Hurry up!

663
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:06,980
Hurry!

664
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:06,840
Sell it.

665
00:30:06,930 --> 00:30:07,650
Mine!

666
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:08,270
Sell them all.

667
00:30:08,270 --> 00:30:09,670
You want to sell them all?

668
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:11,390
Don't panic. Listen to me.

669
00:30:11,970 --> 00:30:15,280
The issuance of this construction treasury bill was led by Central Bank.

670
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,950
The government won't collapse.

671
00:30:16,950 --> 00:30:17,660
Manager.

672
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:18,950
Manager, come here.

673
00:30:18,950 --> 00:30:19,770
Yes, Sir?

674
00:30:19,790 --> 00:30:20,550
Please buy

675
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:22,210
another 100,000 silver dollars worth.

676
00:30:22,210 --> 00:30:23,770
100,000 silver dollars?

677
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:24,480
Are you crazy?

678
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:25,120
No.

679
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,040
So much?

680
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:28,850
I want half of all available stock. Quick.

681
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:40,880
Sir.

682
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:43,470
A telegram from the president.

683
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:44,260
Read it.

684
00:30:46,670 --> 00:30:48,420
I've received an urgent order from the chairman of the board

685
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:50,820
to go to South America for economic research.

686
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:52,790
The construction treasury bills is about to collapse.

687
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:55,320
With your temper, you will find out the truth.

688
00:30:55,340 --> 00:30:56,660
But the truth behind it

689
00:30:57,820 --> 00:30:59,550
must not be known to the public.

690
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:01,340
Otherwise, it will shake people's confidence,

691
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,760
damage the government's reputation,

692
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:04,620
and the credibility of the board.

693
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:07,960
I hope you, Shen Tunan, can establish a Reparations Committee,

694
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:10,160
and deal with this matter appropriately.

695
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:12,080
Please consider and prioritize the bigger picture.

696
00:31:12,080 --> 00:31:13,080
Please remember.

697
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:14,350
Please remember.

698
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:16,700
Credibility?

699
00:31:35,170 --> 00:31:36,170
Credibility.

700
00:33:29,470 --> 00:33:31,150
Investigate the mastermind!

701
00:33:31,230 --> 00:33:32,890
Investigate the mastermind!

702
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:36,000
This is a heinous crime!

703
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:38,870
He must not be forgiven!

704
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:42,380
Safeguard our financial stability!

705
00:33:42,250 --> 00:33:47,330
[Fooling the people]

706
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,260
Investigate the mastermind!

707
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:46,290
Investigate the mastermind!

708
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:47,650
This is a heinous crime!

709
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:49,150
This is a heinous crime!

710
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:51,990
On behalf of the Treasury Department,

711
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:55,040
we would like to extend our sympathies to all of you.

712
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:58,790
At the same time, we would like to

713
00:33:58,810 --> 00:34:02,650
provide clarifications with regards to certain situations.

714
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:07,920
We ask that the public take a rational view of all investments.

715
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:12,639
The construction treasury bills do not involve backroom deals,

716
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:15,449
and any transaction is completely personal.

717
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:19,300
I believe the people of the Republic of China are responsible.

718
00:34:19,770 --> 00:34:23,000
and can take responsibility for their own behavior.

719
00:34:23,389 --> 00:34:26,230
I urge the public

720
00:34:26,350 --> 00:34:29,480
to return to their production lives as soon as possible,

721
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:33,710
and work hard for a more prosperous

722
00:34:33,739 --> 00:34:34,800
Republic of China.

723
00:34:35,429 --> 00:34:36,710
How dare they say that?

724
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:39,020
What else do they dare not?

725
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:40,830
So shameless!

726
00:34:40,860 --> 00:34:42,139
I heard that on the day of the collapse,

727
00:34:42,139 --> 00:34:43,320
several trucks went to the stock exchange that night

728
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,560
to haul all the money.

729
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:46,440
They were recruited from the military at the last minute.

730
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:47,989
Jiang took the people's hard-earned money,

731
00:34:47,989 --> 00:34:51,989
and is going to use that money to buy guns and besiege the Jiangxi Soviet.

732
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:54,360
Our greatest enemy, the Japanese, is at our doors but he's not concerned.

733
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,960
All he knows is to "besiege".

734
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,980
What is he thinking?

735
00:34:59,580 --> 00:35:01,060
After the Mukden Incident,

736
00:35:01,060 --> 00:35:02,240
resisting foreign aggression and securing domestic power

737
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:04,760
has formed the basic national policy of the Kuomintang.

738
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:05,890
Jiang said

739
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,260
removing decay prevents moth-eaten clothing.

740
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:10,260
Those words are still ringing in my ears.

741
00:35:10,260 --> 00:35:12,460
They've become huge moths themselves.

742
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,950
I'm a little worried about Wei Ruolai.

743
00:35:15,950 --> 00:35:16,870
This time,

744
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:19,300
Nanjing will definitely force the Central Bank to take the blame.

745
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:21,180
My brother can't bear the pressure.

746
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:22,240
Being next in line,

747
00:35:22,410 --> 00:35:24,400
it means Wei Ruolai will have to execute the details.

748
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,320
If he does so,

749
00:35:25,450 --> 00:35:27,510
his hands will be stained with blood,

750
00:35:27,730 --> 00:35:29,460
and become a flaw in his resume.

751
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,560
As long as we can get

752
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:39,470
the list of transactions involving malicious manipulation of securities,

753
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:41,600
we can then reveal the truth.

754
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:45,120
It's just that the stock exchange has been seized.

755
00:35:48,770 --> 00:35:49,620
Seized?

756
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:56,270
This is the building structural plan of the stock exchange.

757
00:35:58,090 --> 00:36:00,000
Find a chance to sneak in,

758
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:04,260
and find the list containing the larger-volume transactions.

759
00:36:05,390 --> 00:36:06,050
Okay.

760
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:22,390
Congyun.

761
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:23,460
Sir.

762
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:24,760
Write a report,

763
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,680
recording every detail of

764
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:28,570
the issuance of the treasury bills,

765
00:36:28,570 --> 00:36:30,290
and hand it over to the Treasury Department.

766
00:36:30,290 --> 00:36:31,170
Central Bank

767
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,960
will not take the blame.

768
00:36:35,330 --> 00:36:36,190
Yes, Sir.

769
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,200
Go back to work.

770
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,200
Sir.

771
00:36:50,940 --> 00:36:52,740
I suggest we compile a list of all the transactions immediately,

772
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:54,340
and track down the mastermind.

773
00:36:54,340 --> 00:36:55,360
We should do it as soon as possible.

774
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:57,890
Otherwise, they might destroy the evidence.

775
00:36:58,850 --> 00:36:59,760
Sir.

776
00:36:59,830 --> 00:37:00,790
Stop hesitating.

777
00:37:00,790 --> 00:37:04,320
The list of large transactions is kept strictly confidential.

778
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,660
They may not be willing to provide.

779
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:08,220
There are exemptions in the case of malicious financial incidents.

780
00:37:08,220 --> 00:37:10,200
We can force the stock exchange to break their confidentiality, Sir.

781
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:11,930
Let it go, Ruolai.

782
00:37:12,270 --> 00:37:13,730
There's too much at stake,

783
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,370
and we can't rush it either.

784
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:16,770
Sir.

785
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:17,650
Right now,

786
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:20,250
what matters most is public opinion.

787
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:22,400
We need to give the public

788
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,890
a reasonable explanation as soon as possible.

789
00:37:23,890 --> 00:37:26,270
If we don't pacify the anger of the people, there will be chaos.

790
00:37:26,270 --> 00:37:27,950
The public will be pacified

791
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,900
if the culprits are caught and punished,

792
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:30,460
Sir.

793
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:31,950
I am guessing that this time, it's still the work of

794
00:37:31,950 --> 00:37:33,680
Zhang Mingquan and Yu Shiqing.

795
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:40,260
I wish it was just them.

796
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:42,460
Then who is it, Sir?

797
00:37:43,290 --> 00:37:46,100
Revealing the truth will incite even greater public outrage.

798
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:49,120
If it gets out of control, the consequences will be unimaginable.

799
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:49,920
Is it Nanjing?

800
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:02,610
It seems that Mr. Song already knew about it.

801
00:38:02,610 --> 00:38:04,340
Mr. Song is still trustworthy.

802
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:07,200
Then is it someone even higher up, Sir?

803
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:07,840
Who is it?

804
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,320
Stop guessing, Wei Ruolai.

805
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:10,520
Stop guessing.

806
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:11,880
If we reveal the truth,

807
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,970
it's not just a few minions who are in trouble this time.

808
00:38:13,970 --> 00:38:15,340
Our people will be completely disappointed

809
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:16,220
in our country.

810
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:18,150
The international community will also lose confidence in us.

811
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:20,050
Our party-state has just established a form of unification.

812
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:21,510
All the more reason to...

813
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:22,880
We're working on constructing infrastructure.

814
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,040
All the more reason to get rid of the old and bring in the new.

815
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:25,200
You can get sepsis if

816
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:26,640
you don't pick out an abscess.

817
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:27,680
If we don't fight now, the Central Bank's credibility

818
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,520
will be completely crushed.

819
00:38:28,520 --> 00:38:30,920
What I am doing now is to protect the credibility of Central Bank.

820
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:32,240
Are we defending our credibility with lies, Sir?

821
00:38:32,240 --> 00:38:33,280
At least we leave ourselves a lifeline.

822
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,400
This mountain has tigers and wolves who will devour our people's flesh and blood.

823
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:37,000
What's the use of keeping it?

824
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:46,840
I'm really ashamed to be part of this mountain.

825
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:48,550
What did you say?

826
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:51,820
You want to quit?

827
00:38:59,370 --> 00:39:00,680
Sir, I thought about resigning

828
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:02,490
during the case of the counterfeit coins.

829
00:39:02,490 --> 00:39:04,890
But I'd listened to you, and I have endured.

830
00:39:07,410 --> 00:39:09,270
I can't take it anymore this time.

831
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:11,020
I'm sorry, Sir.

832
00:39:11,350 --> 00:39:12,880
I, Ruolai, hereby resigns.

833
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:13,710
I'm sorry.

834
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:16,260
Wei Ruolai.

835
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:18,220
Wei Ruolai!

836
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:44,560
Liar!

837
00:40:44,830 --> 00:40:45,950
You're all liars!

838
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:46,900
Wen!

839
00:40:47,350 --> 00:40:48,230
Wen!

840
00:40:48,250 --> 00:40:50,040
Give me back my money!

841
00:40:50,490 --> 00:40:51,590
You stay right there!

842
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:52,430
Wen!

843
00:41:00,790 --> 00:41:01,650
Give me back my money!

844
00:41:01,650 --> 00:41:03,250
Wen!

845
00:41:03,790 --> 00:41:04,630
Liar!

846
00:41:04,980 --> 00:41:06,230
-Wen!
-Give me back my money!

847
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:06,990
Don't come over!

848
00:41:06,990 --> 00:41:07,880
Don't come over!

849
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:08,280
Back off!

850
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:08,720
Don't move!

851
00:41:08,720 --> 00:41:09,250
Back off!

852
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,280
I'll jump if you come any closer!

853
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,030
Okay, I won't move.

854
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:11,710
I won't move.

855
00:41:11,710 --> 00:41:13,310
You said we could make money.

856
00:41:13,600 --> 00:41:14,480
Where is the money?

857
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,590
Why did you lie to me?

858
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:16,220
I'm not lying.

859
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,130
Wen, come down.

860
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:18,880
You said I could buy!

861
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:19,540
Yes, I did.

862
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:21,180
But I told you not to borrow money.

863
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,670
-You said we could make money.
-Come down.

864
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:23,670
The radio said so,

865
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:24,680
the newspaper also said so,

866
00:41:24,680 --> 00:41:26,040
you said so, Ms. Zhou said so too.

867
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:27,760
Everyone said we could make money.

868
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:28,840
Why did you lie to me?

869
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:30,120
We can pay back your debts slowly.

870
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:30,690
Come down first.

871
00:41:30,690 --> 00:41:31,680
There's no future.

872
00:41:31,680 --> 00:41:33,340
The debt collectors are here.

873
00:41:33,380 --> 00:41:35,640
Not only did I lose all the money I earned,

874
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:38,170
I also owe them hundreds of silver dollars.

875
00:41:38,170 --> 00:41:39,530
A few hundreds!

876
00:41:39,550 --> 00:41:40,520
How could I ever pay them back?

877
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:42,600
I couldn't pay it back even if I worked so hard that my legs broke.

878
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:44,310
I can't even pay the interest.

879
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,560
I'll pay it back for you.

880
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:47,010
I'll pay them back for you.

881
00:41:47,010 --> 00:41:48,800
I'll catch all those bastards,

882
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:49,710
and I'll pay them back for you.

883
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:51,030
Come down, Man.

884
00:41:51,140 --> 00:41:52,440
I'll do you justice.

885
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,080
You can't fight them at all.

886
00:41:54,850 --> 00:41:56,390
Look at what happened to the case of counterfeit coins.

887
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:58,790
So many brothers died in vain.

888
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:01,800
What's going to happen even if you hold it in?

889
00:42:02,020 --> 00:42:03,710
We can't do anything

890
00:42:04,610 --> 00:42:05,940
but watch them cheat us

891
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:08,950
out of all our hard-earned money.

892
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:10,960
Those bastards...

893
00:42:11,750 --> 00:42:15,540
They didn't plan to spare us at all.

894
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:16,080
Man.

895
00:42:17,690 --> 00:42:19,100
Get down first, Man.

896
00:42:19,300 --> 00:42:19,990
Wei.

897
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,300
You are a sheep, not a wolf.

898
00:42:23,610 --> 00:42:24,540
Just quit early.

899
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:29,180
Otherwise, you'll be eaten by them sooner or later.

900
00:42:41,330 --> 00:42:41,960
Wen!

901
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:43,570
Wen!

902
00:42:43,950 --> 00:42:44,670
Wen!
